CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 2, 2010

[Cite as 12/02/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-5836.]

*1450MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-1609. In re Broom.

In Habeas Corpus. On petition for writ of habeas corpus of Romell Broom. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
